OL,3,CDecision due in appeal over Kneecap
OL,4,Crapper's terror case
OL,6,FJudges are set to give their decision
OL,7,Fon the Crown Prosecution Service's bid
OL,8,Fto overturn the decision to throw out
OL,9,Fthe terrorism case against Kneecap
OL,10,Frapper Liam Og O hAnnaidh.
OL,12,FThe rapper, who performs under the
OL,13,Fstage name Mo Chara, was accused of
OL,14,Fdisplaying a flag in support of
OL,15,Fproscribed terror organisation
OL,16,FHezbollah at a gig at the O2 Forum in
OL,17,FKentish Town, north London, on
OL,18,FNovember 21 2024.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
