OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773263167
OL,3,CDecision due in appeal over Kneecap
OL,4,Crapper's terror case
OL,6,FThe case was thrown out in September
OL,7,Flast year, with chief magistrate Paul
OL,8,FGoldspring ruling the proceedings were
OL,9,F"instituted unlawfully".
OL,11,FJudge Goldspring had agreed with O
OL,12,FhAnnaidh's lawyers that prosecutors
OL,13,Fneeded to seek the permission of the
OL,14,FAttorney General to charge the rapper
OL,15,Fbefore informing him on May 21 that he
OL,16,Fwould be charged with a terror offence.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773263167
OL,3,CDecision due in appeal over Kneecap
OL,4,Crapper's terror case
OL,6,FThis permission was sought and given
OL,7,Fthe following day, which the court
OL,8,Fheard meant the charge fell outside
OL,9,Fthe six-month timeframe in which
OL,10,Fcriminal charges against a defendant
OL,11,Fcan be brought.
OL,13,FThe Crown Prosecution Service appealed
OL,14,Fagainst the decision at the High Court
OL,15,Fat a hearing in January, with the
OL,16,FKneecap rapper opposing the appeal.
OL,18,FLord Justice Edis and Mr Justice
OL,19,FLinden are now due to give their
OL,20,Fdecision on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
