OL,3,CDecision due in appeal over Kneecap
OL,4,Crapper's terror case
OL,6,FKneecap have previously said they
OL,7,Fwould be holding a press conference
OL,8,Fshortly after the judgment is handed
OL,9,Fdown.
OL,11,FThey continued in an Instagram post:
OL,12,F"We would love to also see supporters
OL,13,Foutside the Mill.
OL,15,F"We are forever grateful for the
OL,16,Fimmense support we have received
OL,17,Fthroughout the world during this
OL,18,Fentire witch-hunt, especially the
OL,19,Fthousands of people who gathered in
OL,20,FLondon.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@AOU
