PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773263167
OL,3,CDecision due in appeal over Kneecap
OL,4,Crapper's terror case
OL,6,F"We have always said we would fight
OL,7,Fthem in their own courts and we would
OL,8,Fwin... Let's see if we have."
OL,10,FThe group signed off with "free
OL,11,FPalestine", and "free the six
OL,12,Fcounties".
OL,14,FThe High Court judgment will be handed
OL,15,Fdown remotely at 2pm on Wednesday.
